# 🔧 Doorstep Device Repair — Real-World Enhancement Plan

## Overview

Transform the existing MVP into a **real-world Rapido/Swiggy-style service marketplace** with:
- Technician KYC verification (Aadhaar/PAN/Govt ID) with **admin-gated registration**
- Workshop/shop photo verification with GPS proximity validation
- Geo-based nearby technician discovery & order broadcast
- **Capacitor-powered mobile + web** app with background location tracking
- Configurable slot booking limits (admin-controlled)
- Removal of online payment and price estimation (app acts as pure middleware)
- **Subscription model** (placeholder — currently free for all, ready for future monetization)

