## Resolved Decisions

| Decision | Resolution |
|---|---|
| **Payment Removal** | ✅ Confirmed. Remove all pricing, invoices, and payment logic. App is pure middleware — customer & technician negotiate pricing offline. |
| **Location Tracking** | ✅ **Capacitor Geolocation** for both web and mobile. Background location service on native (Android/iOS), periodic foreground ping on web. "Go Online" toggle + continuous GPS updates. |
| **KYC API Integration** | ✅ **Manual admin review** for now. Technician uploads docs → Admin reviews → Approves/Rejects. Placeholder for future automated API (Surepass/IDfy). |
| **Registration Gating** | ✅ **Admin-gated**. Technician registers → Uploads KYC + shop → Admin reviews & approves → Only then registration is "complete" and technician can receive orders. |
| **Workshop Validation** | ✅ **Admin visual review + GPS proximity check**. Photos auto-tagged with current GPS. Admin sees map overlay of photo location vs. registered shop address. Flagged if distance > 500m. |
| **Admin Panel** | ✅ **Separate admin dashboard app/module**. All admin features (KYC review, shop verification, config management) in a dedicated separate app, not in the existing Angular customer/technician module. |
| **Verification Timing** | ✅ **Register → Upload docs → Admin reviews → Approved → Can go online**. Technician is blocked from the dashboard until admin approves. |
| **Subscription Model** | ✅ **Placeholder for future**. Currently free for both customers and technicians. Schema and architecture prepared for future subscription tiers. |

> [!WARNING]
> **Breaking Change**: Existing orders in the database with invoice/quote data will remain untouched, but the UI to view them will be removed. Any in-progress orders with quoted prices will lose their display.

